task.summary: First commit Add C++ support Add required dependencies Add division by packages Add release and debug directories with their respective SDMessagesApp implementations Add required permissions in manifest Add integration with Fabric crashlytics Add integration with Google Play Services Add utility and base classes

Add pepper in native C code Create Hasher, which is a hash generator used to hash passwords to make them more secure, with its implementation and test Create S3FilesManager, which abstract the AWS classes to upload files to the server, with implementation Create ImageCompressor to compress images(files) without losing quality before sending them to the server Add room AppDatabase with UserDao and GroupDao Add PreferencesHelper to save some recurrently used data(isLogged, userId and sessionId) Add model data classes necessary for the room db Add retrofit SDMessagesApi to access to the server rest api for online functionality Add UserRepository for interaction with the room db models and rest api Add utility class PermissionsManager to manage permissions like a boss Add ActivityBuilder for activities and fragments dagger graph Add several modules for app dependencies Add login feature with LogInActivity and LogInViewModel Add sign up feature with SignUpActivity, RegisterActivity and RegisterViewModel [NOTE: this is improvable] Add some more utility classes and resources files
